import React from 'react'
import LeftSidebar from './LeftSidebar'
import Mainbar from './Mainbar'
import RightSidebar from './RightSidebar'
import { StyledApp } from './styles/App.styled'

const Dashboard = () => {
  return (
    <StyledApp>
      <LeftSidebar />
      <Mainbar />
      <RightSidebar />
    </StyledApp>
  )
}

export default Dashboard
